uct-info\">\n                    <h3>Byte Backpack</h3>\n                    <p>Carry your essentials in this spacious and tech-themed backpack.</p>\n                    <div class=\"price\">$45.00</div>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"buy-button\">Add to Cart</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Playful Bytes. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>\n            <a href=\"#\">About Us</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\">Contact</a> |\n            <a href=\"#\">Privacy Policy</a>\n        </p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple animation for product cards on hover is handled by CSS\n        // Can add more JS interactions here if needed in the future\n        console.log(\"Playful Bytes website loaded!\");\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"}